sudo mv 1x1.png 
/usr/share/kodi/addons/skin.estouchy/media/pointer_1x1.png
custome skin is in:
/home/osmc/.kodi/addons/

sudo nano /home/osmc/.kodi/addons/skin.re-touched/16x9/Pointer.xml

And replace all "width" and "height" values with 1 and all "texture" values with the name of the 1x1 texture:

<width>1</width>
<height>1</height>
<texture>pointer_1x1.png</texture>
